  "description": {
   "en": "“Give your life to me, and I’ll help you forget a person.” As a result, countless people go for it and use part of their life to exchange for a peaceful life. Heartbroken past is hidden in the hairpin of the imperial noble consort and the spiritual sword of the stylite.\n\n“Don’t you even have someone that you want to forget?”\n\n“Yeah, but I’ve already forgotten him.”\n\n---\n**Alternate Raws:** [iQiyi Manhua](https://www.iqiyi.com/manhua/detail_18yzm972cl.html), [U17](https://www.u17.com/comic/182884.html), [Yizhikan](https://www.yizhikan.com/comic/13030), [Zymk](https://www.zymk.cn/3669/)\n**Official Translations:** [English (Webcomics)](https://www.webcomicsapp.com/comic/5dc271148c252b053a3b6896), [English (Flying Lines)](https://www.flying-lines.com/comic/memory-erasing-bell)\nOfficial Animated Version: [Ake Animation on YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLokmx9AcsdTfyWucgbtnaHVp1sdvfoQsJ)  \nOfficial Subtitled Version: [S1](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLo11RdjLkdJCnxPC3o10Syk53nsqBhJk_)"
